title: Power Music Friday ( Sean Kingston  and Sinqua Walls)
itunes:title: Power Music Friday ( Sean Kingston  and Sinqua Walls)
description:
Today on the show we had Sinqua Walls from Power stopped by to speak on new acting roles, intimate scenes, individual growth and more. Also, we had Sean Kingston call in to speak on new music, beautiful girls, Soulja Boy, NBA YoungBoy and more. Moreover, Charlamagne, gave "Donkey of the Day" to the Arkansas department of health for their commercial on convincing people to get vaccinated.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
